{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Space Calibrator is a tool to allow you to use multiple vendors' devices together in SteamVR! </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use full body trackers with Meta Quest / Pico VR headsets. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use Valve Index Controllers with Meta Quest / Pico VR headsets. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use Vive Ultimate Trackers with SteamVR headsets (e.g. Valve Index). </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Standard Calibration</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Calibrate play spaces by moving a controller and a tracker together in an infinity sign. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Continuous calibration</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Attach a tracker on your VR headset to align play spaces together automatically. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0     <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368750/extras/Standard_Calibration.gif?t=1739530850\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368750/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739530850","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368750/page.bg.jpg?t=1739530850","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368750/c773096d1b165621b3475c722cb0adcfe6233c46/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739530850","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368750/c773096d1b165621b3475c722cb0adcfe6233c46/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739530850","categories":[{"description":"VR Only","id":54}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Space Calibrator is a tool to allow you to use multiple vendors' devices together in